      • getDomainResultResultJavaType

        Class<R> getDomainResultResultJavaType()
        The type actually returned from this reader's readRow(org.hibernate.sql.results.jdbc.spi.RowProcessingState, org.hibernate.sql.results.jdbc.spi.JdbcValuesSourceProcessingOptions) call, accounting for any transformers.

        May be null to indicate that no transformation is applied.

        Ultimately intended for use in comparing values are being de-duplicated
